pace, I love that the Litter-Robot Evo has a very compact footprint. And instead of pressing buttons all day, although look at that nice LCD display, instead I can sit back and relax and control the Litter-Robot Evo from afar through the Whisker app, which allows you to monitor your cat's bathroom habits and check waste store levels, which gives me a lot of peace of mind. And it has quiet-sift technology, which is quite nice because it's right next to my desk. Since the Litter-Robot Evo basically runs on autopilot, I can spend more time doing the things I love. So if you're a cat parent looking to have an even more relaxing summer, check out the Litter-Robot Evo."}]}